# ForkFlow-CRM: Food Broker CRM System

## Project Context
You are helping build ForkFlow-CRM, a website-first, mobile UI friendly CRM for food brokers who visit restaurants and stores. This is a learning project for a new developer.

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS + react-admin
- Backend: Supabase (PostgreSQL, Auth, Storage, REST API)
- Maps: Google Maps JavaScript API
- UI Components: shadcn/ui, DaisyUI, Tremor charts
- No Docker required - cloud-only development

## Core Features
- Customer management (restaurants, grocery stores, distributors)
- Visit tracking with GPS coordinates
- Follow-up reminder system
- Mobile-optimized interface with 44px+ touch targets
- Maps integration for customer locations

## Learning Goals
- Always explain TypeScript concepts when using them
- Show React best practices and modern patterns
- Demonstrate proper database design principles
- Teach mobile-first responsive design
